title: DDFP TV Week 12
itunes:title: DDFP TV Week 12
description:
In this special edition podcast, Dave Dameshek lists the most valuable players in the league using his “Jenga Theory” and ponders RGIII’s future in Washington. Plus, Elliot Harrison helps preview Week 12 with “The Greatest Moments in NFL Hookup History” and Football Baby is back for more game picks.
